<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7993152>
    dc:description "FIG.3. Hymenaster giboryi (124131-B79): a. Abactinal general view. Scale bar: 2.5 mm. b.Anus. Spine’s wreath. Scale bar: 2.5 mm. c. Actinal general view. Adambulacral plates and furrow spines. Scale bar: 2.5 mm. d. Adambulacral spines detail. Scale bar: 2.5 mm. Map. World distribution area of some species of the genus Hymenaster (see legend)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7993152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

